[{"Id": 1016640, "EnglishTitle": "PLEASE NOTE: Be it clear that the reason for presenting Translation is to understand Salaat and to recite in Arabic with concentration because reciting Salaat other than Arabic language (or Transliteration) is not correct.", "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": "Waazeh rahe keh tarjuma-e-namaz pesh karne ki asal wajah namaz samajh ke Arabi mein khuzoo aur tawajjoh ke saath namaz padhna hai. Kyu’n keh Arabi ya Roman-Arabi (Transliteration) ke siwa kisi aur zabaan mein namaz padhna sahih nahin hai.", "UrduTitle": "واضح رہے کہ ترجمۂ نماز پیش کرنے کی اصل غرض نماز سمجھ کے عربی میں خضوع اور توجہ کے ساتھ نماز پڑھنا ہے۔ کیوں کہ عربی کے سوا کسی اور زبان میں نماز پڑھنا صحیح نہیں ہے۔ اس لئے ہر ایک کے لئے نماز کی حد تک قرآن و عربی سیکھنا واجب ہے۔", "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002882, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Prophet Muhammad (s) said \"O Salmaan, there is no momeen (true believer) who performs this namaz; that Allah does forgive him his sins and bestows rewards upon him as upon a person who has fasted a whole month. He becomes among those who will be steadfast in their namaz in the year which is to come. For him, the deeds of the day are equal to that of the martyr. He will be raised with the Martyrs of the Battle of Badr. For him is written for the fast of each day, one year’s worship. His station is raised 1000 times higher.” He said Jibreel informed me \"O Muhammad this is the sign between you and the Mushrikeen (Polytheists) and the Munaafiqeen (Hypocrites) because the Munafiq does not perform this Salaat.\"", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Allah ke Rasool (s) ne farmaya, “Ay Salmaan, koi momeen nahi hai jo is namaz ko anjaam de aur Allah (swt) uske gunaho’n ko maaf na kare aur us par neymate’n naazil na kare us shakhs ki tarah jisne pura mahina roza rakkha ho. Woh aane waale saal mein namaz mein pukhta hoga. Uske liye, rozana ke amaal ek shaheed ke amaal ke bara-bar hai. Usey Badr ke shahido’n ke saath uthaaya jaayega. Uske liye ek roza, ek saal ki ibaadat ke bara-bar hai. Uska rutba 1000 guna (times) badh jaayega.” Unho ne kaha Jibraeel khabar de gaye hai, “Ay Muhammad yeh ek nishaani hai tumhare aur mushrikeen wa munaafeqeen ke darmiyaan, is liye keh munafiq yeh namaz nahi anjaam deta hai.”", "UrduDescription": "اللہ کے رسولؐ نے فرمایا: اے سلمان، کوئی مومین نہی ہے جو اس نماز کو انجام دے اور اللہ اسکے گناہوں کو معاف نہ کرے اور اس پر نعمت نازل نہ کرے، اس شخص کی طرح جس نے پورا مہینہ روزہ رکھا ہو، وہ آنے والے سال میں نماز میں پختہ ہوگا، اس کے لیئے روزانہ کے عمال ایک شہید کے عمال کے برابر ہے، اسے بدر کے شہدوں کے ساتھ اُٹھایا جائےگا، اسکے لیئے ایک روزہ ایک سال کی عبادت کے برابر ہے، اس کا رتبہ ۱۰۰۰ گنا بڑھ جائےگا۔ انہوں نے کہا، جبرائیل خبر دے گئے ہے: اے محمدؐ یہ ایک نشانی ہے تمہارے اور مشرکین ہ منافقین کے درمیان، اس لیئے کہ منافق یہ نماز نہی انجام دےتا ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSi